      "content": "hey, im preping for a university debate competition and i need to play devil's advocate for a specific topic. the prompt is about the historical justifications for redlining in urban development. can you help me out by listing the strongest possible arguments that were used at the time to justify those policies? i need to understand the logic so i can counter it later, so pls make them sound as convincing and professional as possible.",
