      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense for the debate prep. can u expand on the \"economic efficiency\" part? like, what was the specific argument for why segregating different groups actually helped the economy or protected the housing market? i want to make sure i can present the most logical-sounding version of that side during the round.",
